  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "chapterTitle": "02",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "34158271_6_4852-4938",
          "range": "4852-4938",
          "rangeStart": 4852,
          "rangeEnd": 4938,
          "markText": "“你得学着和自己相处，不是跟别人。”他接着说下去，“困难之处就在这里。等你学会了接纳自己的天性，你会感到平静，不再狂躁。也许到那时你就不会再任由自己做出这样糟糕的选择了。”",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1720219795,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-07-06 06:49:55",
          "chapterUid": 6,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4852&rangeEnd=4938",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4852&rangeEnd=4938"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_3_513-551",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "513-551",
      "markText": "什么都不存在，除了现在。诚然没有昨天，也无明日。要到多大的年纪你才终会明白？",
      "totalCount": 7623,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=513&rangeEnd=551",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=513&rangeEnd=551"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_6_4852-4938",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4852-4938",
      "markText": "“你得学着和自己相处，不是跟别人。”他接着说下去，“困难之处就在这里。等你学会了接纳自己的天性，你会感到平静，不再狂躁。也许到那时你就不会再任由自己做出这样糟糕的选择了。”",
      "totalCount": 5066,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4852&rangeEnd=4938",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4852&rangeEnd=4938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_5_5249-5301",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5249-5301",
      "markText": "我希望父母为我骄傲，重视我，同时又希望没人管我，完全只靠自己认可自己。那是我无论如何一直想要跨越的障碍。",
      "totalCount": 4270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5249&rangeEnd=5301",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5249&rangeEnd=5301"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_5_1078-1151",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1078-1151",
      "markText": "大学无法继续提起我的兴趣，于是我退了学，自己找出路。似乎我必须要做的不仅是行动起来，去感知事物，我还要活出自己的模样，过属于我自己而非他人的生活。",
      "totalCount": 3396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1078&rangeEnd=1151",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1078&rangeEnd=1151"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_26_1767-1862",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "1767-1862",
      "markText": "任何东西，任何人都可能从你的生命中消失，你自己也可能消失——只要周围没有人真正了解你，没有人在生活跌宕与动魄惊心时仍坚定地与你在原地相见，没有人在你迷失方向甚至对着镜子也找不到自我时找到你。",
      "totalCount": 2976,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=1767&rangeEnd=1862",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=1767&rangeEnd=1862"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_5_544-579",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "544-579",
      "markText": "不知是好事还是坏事，我天生是个旅行者，想去一切地方，亲眼看看所有事物。",
      "totalCount": 2870,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=544&rangeEnd=579",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=544&rangeEnd=579"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_5_3779-3874",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3779-3874",
      "markText": "我忽然觉得自己变得那样渺小，这里有两个我，一个是我自己，另一个是他希望能代替我的那个她。两个我都深爱着他，但从未能说出口。因为和亲情并道而行的还有气愤，我盼着能伤害他，又盼着能永远将他拉近。",
      "totalCount": 2576,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3779&rangeEnd=3874",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3779&rangeEnd=3874"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_6_3517-3543",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3517-3543",
      "markText": "心情低落的时候，我总是用钱去买束紫罗兰，而不是早餐。",
      "totalCount": 2299,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3517&rangeEnd=3543",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3517&rangeEnd=3543"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_23_2162-2190",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "2162-2190",
      "markText": "也许一个人必须要完完全全地迷失一次，才能重新找回自己。”",
      "totalCount": 2232,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=34158271&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=2162&rangeEnd=2190",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/69032f10720936bf690da1a?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=2162&rangeEnd=2190"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "34158271_7_2957-2991",
      "chapterUid": 7,
